description: There’s been a jailbreak and Kenny hunts down the Warden to take revenge for the tickle tortment he suffered in jail. Tony, the Warden, is relaxing at home when Kenny breaks in and makes him to get down on his knees and worship his smelly socks. Kenny has been traveling miles on foot and his feet and socks are sweaty. After that Kenny humiliates his Warden more by making him suck his perfect toes and clean his feet with his tongue.
title: Kenny Worshiped By The Warden
